@shane this is Season 11 the way the DVDs are sold is buy Volume. 
Volume 1 is Season 1 and 2
Volume 2 is Season 3
Volume 3 is the first half of Season 4
Volume 4 is the second half of Season 4
Volume 5,6,7,8 are the same respective Seasons 5,6,7,8
Volume 9 is the first half of Season 9
Volume 10 is the second half of season 9
Volume 11 is actually Season 10 
so no the file is not labeled Wrong
